text: Phoebemima teteia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1996. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Phoebemima teteia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1996
